#: 21337012-0-993
msgctxt "21337012-0-993"
msgid "To the Almightly Almsivi,"
"\n"
"\nWatch over my family. I pray that those who are healthy remain safe, while those who are ill soon gain entrance to the quarantine. I received a token and am blessed. Soon I will get the cure. May the Three speed the elixir so that it works swiftly. Then my family may be united once more."
"\n"
"\nEver faithful,"
"\n"
"\nRuthri Othrenim"
msgstr ""

