#: 21337012-0-407
msgctxt "21337012-0-407"
msgid "Dear Johun,"
"\n"
"\nAre you keeping warm? I hope so. I started to write about how much I miss you, but now I have something else to tell you. I met someone. I'm sorry to break it to you this way, but I couldn't wait to tell you. "
"\n"
"\nHe's a Dark Elf, an envoy with the Ebonheart Pact. He came into the forge and we started talking. One thing led to another, and … well, you know. "
"\n"
"\nHe's exotic and exciting. And he's very good to me. "
"\n"
"\nWell, I need to go now. Bye!"
"\n"
"\n— Idesa"
