msgid "Note to Cardia"
msgstr ""

#: 21337012-0-1464
msgctxt "21337012-0-1464"
msgid "Dearest Father, "
"\n"
"\nI hope you can understand—Darius is just so handsome and kind! He's not like the other Sphinxmoth Bandits. He just wants to save up enough to buy a farm for the two of us. Please understand why I had to go with him. And please, I beg you, father—don't try to follow us. These are dangerous people and I don't want you to get hurt. "
"\n"
"\nYour Loving Daughter, "
"\n"
"\nCardia"
"\n"
"\nP.S. I'm sorry about taking mother's ring, but Darius didn't have enough money to buy an engagement ring."
