msgctxt "21337012-0-1411"
msgid "My Dearest Beautiful Zali,"
"\n"
"\nI saw you by the water again. The sun made your silver fur light up like it was a bright day. I would have stood there forever, but I stand a lot guarding the embassy so I left."
