msgid "Leofa,"
"\n"
"\nJust thought you should know that ""your"" Companion doesn't love you. He loves adventure and danger and killing things and getting his name scrawled on their damn walls. But he doesn't love YOU. Not the way I love you and have always loved you and will always love you."
"\n"
"\nWhen you finally come to your senses, you know where to find me."
"\n"
"\nLove,"
"\n"
"\nUggald"
